      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I am so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been a bit obsessive about keeping it spotless and perfectly maintained, so it looks and drives like a dream. If you've been looking for that 'perfect' find that\u2019s been loved and babied since day one, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
