    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform, offering a visceral driving experience defined by its 3.2L inline-six and individual throttle bodies. The engine exhibits flawless compression and a meticulously maintained VANOS system, ensuring peak torque delivery across the power band. The chassis has been proactively addressed with subframe reinforcement and features a refreshed suspension geometry for razor-sharp turn-in. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a tight limited-slip differential. Finished in a concourse-level aesthetic with original paint depth and a pristine interior, this specimen represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated BMW engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
