    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman, finished in iconic Guards Red over a pristine Black leather interior. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint is entirely original, displaying a deep, mirror-like finish free of swirl marks, stone chips, or any road rash. The 19-inch Boxster S wheels are flawless and come wrapped in a fresh set of N-rated Pirelli P Zero tires. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, the switchgear remains crisp to the touch, and the interior still possesses that signature factory-fresh scent. Mechanically, this Cayman is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history exclusively through Porsche authorized technicians. Every fluid flush and inspection has been performed on schedule, ensuring the turbocharged powertrain and PDK transmission operate with absolute precision. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a modern sports car that has been preserved with the utmost care. Sale includes the original window sticker, two keys, and all service documentation.",
      "price": 48900.0,
